data.description: Charming 3BR, 1.5BA home on a vast .68 acre lot close to downtown Ridgeland offering both peace & proximity. Step inside & be greeted by an inviting living area, perfect for relaxing and entertaining guests. The adjacent dining area flows seamlessly into the well-appointed kitchen. The primary bedroom offers a peaceful retreat, while the 2 additional bedrooms provide comfortable spaces for family members or guests. The Full bathroom is conveniently located near the BRs for easy access, and the half bath adds an extra level of convenience The Large fenced backyard offers a secure haven for kids, pets & events.
